title: Moodies
description:
My Almost Complete collection of the Moody Blues.

Contains all the studio albums and 2 Justin Hayward solo albums, 1 Ray Thomas solo and the Blue Jays album by Justin Hayward & John lodge.

Sorry to anyone that looked at my last (unsuccessful) attempt to upload a torrent for the Moodies. Hopefully this one will be OK.

Regards.
